Filming of the Czech comedy Theory of the Tiger has ended.
The last straw in the main character's resolution is the voluntary death of his father-in-law, who has run out of strength and patience.
Grandma - Iva Janžurová decided about her grandfather's life, old age and funeral.
It is clear to Jan that he is with his wife Olga - Eliška Balzerová on a similar journey.
He remembers that he once had his own will and dreams, and he wants to live with dignity and freedom again.
He longs to regain control of his life - and as a solution he chooses to escape from the existing one, Nightingale said about the story.
Bajgar wanted to capture in a comedy form a certain type of relationship in which one of the partners does not feel completely free.
From the beginning, it was clear that the main role would fall to Bartošek, with whom he had already worked on the series Invisible.
Nevertheless, the actor, who appeared in front of the camera after a long break associated with recovery from a serious illness, surprised him.
We agreed three years ago.
